data.description: Welcome to Copper Creek, a gated community that includes a clubhouse with gym, pool, basketball, tennis, playground, sidewalks and street lights. Allapattah Flats K-8 elementary school is just outside the gates of the community.  2 Story home with first floor primary bedroom with 2 closets and large bathroom. Open kitchen, dining and living room. Formal living or dining room and half bath. Second floor has ensuite bedroom and bath and last 2 bedrooms have a ''jack and jill'' bath and loft. 2 car garage and inside laundry room.
